{"tid":1905640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長者交通優惠(2蚊車)=政府資助散播病毒","createTime":"2020-03-01T11:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T09:32:45.000Z","uid":172423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cab38875188ac32e5cd79c6e1e9ffb1824d33065","tid":1905640,"uid":172423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:39:20.000Z","msg":"1. <span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span>為抗疫，一方面<span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲市民</span><br />\n- 減少社會接觸<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">減少外出</span>及社交活動<br />\n2. 65歲以上確診者高達<span style=\"color: red;\">34%</span><br />\n3. 一方面繼續<span style=\"color: red;\">資助長者</span>，以<span style=\"color: red;\">2蚊</span>車費<span style=\"color: red;\">全港遊</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">論點︰既然政府在疫情嚴峻其間，仍要打工仔受感染威脅下返工，為何不暫緩長者交通優惠，減低公共交通系統負荷，減少擠迫情況！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.1 減少社會接觸<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/31/P2020013100768.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202001%2F31%2FP2020013100768.htm&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGoh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=9b0c5f3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/31/P2020013100768.htm</a><br />\n1.2 減少人流及社交接觸機會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/01/P2020020100466.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202002%2F01%2FP2020020100466.htm&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGoh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=4e19df3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202002/01/P2020020100466.htm</a><br />\n2.1 頭96宗確診者中，65歲以上確診者佔34%<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7cYfZpK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7cYfZpK.jpg&h=1b4ddb35&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n3.1 政府65歲或以上長者及合資格殘疾人士 公共交通票價優惠計劃 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/gov_public_transport_fare_concession/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fgov_public_transport_fare_concession%2Findex.html&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGoh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=f2d2aa31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/gov_public_transport_fare_concession/index.html</a><br />\n3.2 長者全港四處外出<br />\n3.2.1 福慧精舍幾乎全部65歲或以上<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2881728835246051/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F2881728835246051%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGoh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=93896306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2881728835246051/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n3.2.2 第98宗個案：71歲女子 多次出席福慧精舍活動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n待續..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e026d7e6128dfd584fc3273abad28d8acd779285","tid":1905640,"uid":172423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"c849e3aba7b0707d5afb883bcc7929dbc128c097","tid":1905640,"uid":322703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個提議幾好"},{"pid":"959ee881af103e5d95bf451494c5ff69906ea291","tid":1905640,"uid":172423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:06:06.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"54b16b9187a3e7c0b0b4350c73060343628cc942","tid":1905640,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fba2eb37dc3e4aee35d6b92a29309fb3fafeeb","tid"